Summarise the missingness in each variable

Provide a summary for each variable of the number and percent missings, ordering by the most missings in each variable.

miss_var_summary(data, order = FALSE, ...)

Arguments

data

a data.frame
order

a logical indicating whether or not to order the result by n_miss. TRUE orders from largest to smallest n_miss, and FALSE orders by order provided by the data.
...

extra arguments

Value

a tibble of the percent of missing data in each variable

See also

miss_case_pct miss_case_prop miss_prop_summary() miss_case_summary miss_case_table miss_summary miss_var_pct miss_var_prop miss_var_run miss_var_span miss_var_table

Examples


miss_var_summary(airquality)
#> # A tibble: 6 x 4
#>   variable n_miss pct_miss n_miss_cumsum
#>   <chr>     <int>    <dbl>         <int>
#> 1 Ozone        37    24.2             37
#> 2 Solar.R       7     4.58            44
#> 3 Wind          0     0               44
#> 4 Temp          0     0               44
#> 5 Month         0     0               44
#> 6 Day           0     0               44
miss_var_summary(oceanbuoys, order = TRUE)
#> # A tibble: 8 x 4
#>   variable   n_miss pct_miss n_miss_cumsum
#>   <chr>       <int>    <dbl>         <int>
#> 1 humidity       93   12.6             177
#> 2 air_temp_c     81   11.0              84
#> 3 sea_temp_c      3    0.408             3
#> 4 year            0    0                 0
#> 5 latitude        0    0                 0
#> 6 longitude       0    0                 0
#> 7 wind_ew         0    0               177
#> 8 wind_ns         0    0               177

# works with group_by from dplyr
library(dplyr)
airquality %>%
  group_by(Month) %>%
  miss_var_summary()
#> # A tibble: 25 x 5
#>    Month variable n_miss pct_miss n_miss_cumsum
#>    <int> <chr>     <int>    <dbl>         <int>
#>  1     5 Ozone         5     16.1             5
#>  2     5 Solar.R       4     12.9             9
#>  3     5 Wind          0      0               9
#>  4     5 Temp          0      0               9
#>  5     5 Day           0      0               9
#>  6     6 Ozone        21     70.0            21
#>  7     6 Solar.R       0      0              21
#>  8     6 Wind          0      0              21
#>  9     6 Temp          0      0              21
#> 10     6 Day           0      0              21
#> # ... with 15 more rows
